5.19 Transfer
=============

This data type defines the transfer protocol. This list can be extended
with other transfer protocols.

Type: Transfer (Enumerated)

.. list-table::
   :widths: 3 5 45
   :header-rows: 1

   * - ID
     - Name
     - Description
   * - 1
     - http
     - HTTP protocol
   * - 2
     - https
     - HTTPS protocol
